==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Marinate
<hw>Mar"i*nate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Marine</er>, and cf. <er>Marinade</er>.]</ety> <def>To salt or
pickle, as fish, and then preserve in oil or vinegar; to prepare (food)
by the use of marinade.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

